name: Alam Tirta Outbound
address: Banjar Samuan Kangin, Carangsari, Kec. Petang, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80353, Indonesia
review 1: Friendly and helpful staffs all around. Good food. Spacious area and parking. Great rafting experience with waterfalls, clear water, lazy river, and some good challenging spots.
review 2: Alam Tirta Outbound is an outdoor adventure and recreation provider located in Banjar Samuan Kangin, Carangsari, Petang District, Badung Regency, Bali, Indonesia. Nestled amidst the serene natural beauty of Bali, Alam Tirta Outbound offers a variety of exciting activities and experiences for individuals, families, and groups.
review 3: Good experience. But not the best. Good quality of services, place, outbound activity. There's so many tap. So u can easily wudhu there.
review 4: Nice view, good for family gathering, company gathering. Big space, and clean facility
review 5: Dissapointing. Looks old and lots of broken items. I wouldnt come back and certainly can‚Äôt recommend it. Too bad considering that we came from so far to go there
